{"tid":878820,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「是日晚餐」文華冰廳黯然銷魂飯！","createTime":"2018-10-27T12:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T02:19:11.000Z","uid":165934,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"24933d3f3ac341b083560d53e4f59114cb21724d","tid":878820,"uid":165934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/201639_7a34f297a053ff431a5cd0aee4e667f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F201639_7a34f297a053ff431a5cd0aee4e667f8.png&h=bce125e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩舊叉燒呢，就夠曬標準啦！<br />\n有燶邊啦，有肥啦，有肉啦，又夠厚切噢！正！<br />\n豉油汁，有老抽啦有生抽啦，又夠香<br />\n蛋呢係燶邊蛋尼嘅，之前嗰啲得一隻，而家有兩隻，抵啲呀！<br />\n飯呢，差少少，腍咗啲，啲飯少啲lor，如果好肚餓嘅朋友就差啲啦<br />\n$65包熱飲，凍飲加$3<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食撚屎啦屌你老母好撚難食呀仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424c057a333ca8c21e86c2a557a528a5c6edad9c","tid":878820,"uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:23:34.000Z","msg":"畀狗食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e7d11e9e97243e9489b204a5d25dbe531ebb1a","tid":878820,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6afd5e3c25c141eb691ad80e04f8ff8cd42b434","tid":878820,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"文華冰廳=垃圾"},{"pid":"a92dd9d436380722bbece39ca478867b9361390f","tid":878820,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T01:09:25.000Z","msg":"咁你又入去食?<br />\n<br />\n明知垃圾?"},{"pid":"01262899e9a7e191c6e257745344503ed734e567","tid":878820,"uid":165934,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a92dd9d436380722bbece39ca478867b9361390f","tid":878820,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"sc